	"Robin_Bubble1": "You're finally here!",
	"Dialog_1_Robin": "@! I'm happy to see you again! It's been a couple months.",
	"Dialog_2_Robin": "I can't believe it's move-in day for you! Everyone in town is excited you're officially a resident of Stardew Valley.",
