	"Dialog_7_Robin": "This is our way of welcoming you to the valley, @!",
	"Dialog_8_Robin": "Lewis is inside the cottage preparing some things for you still.",
	"Dialog_9_Robin": "Since he's busy, this is a good opportunity for me to show you the repaired bridge!",
