	"Dialog_20_Lewis": "I hope the improvements we've made to %farm Farm and your grandpa's cottage will make it easier to get settled in.",
	"Dialog_21_Lewis": "Your furniture and belongings arrived a couple days ago! Everything is inside.",
	"Dialog_22_Lewis": "Robin, did you show @ the improvements out here?",
